  "text": "However, these findings are in contradiction to findings of [CITATION_1] . They acknowledged the marital satisfaction decreases in the early years of marital life because spouses require the time to adapt to a new circumstance. They have to negotiate responsibilities and encounter the realities of marital life. Also, it is noticeable that the majority of participants in all levels of marital satisfaction had a moderate level of finance. In other words, level of finance has not affected level of marital satisfaction for sample of current study.",
